data.description:
Wonderful 4 bed, 2 bath Home w/great curb appeal & 2 car garage. Interior boasts a cozy family area, plush carpet, plantation shutters, French doors into the Arizona room, neutral tile floor, and designer palette throughout. Contemporary kitchen is equipped with ample wood cabinetry, granite countertops, recessed lighting, and stainless steel appliances. Large bedrooms  plush carpet/padding, ample closets,  & pristine baths. Interior laundry room w/storage cabinets. Expansive backyard with grassy landscaping, covered patio, and convenient storage shed to top it all off. Your new home is waiting for you, schedule a showing today!

The Arizona room gives you more square footage to enjoy.  Extra storage on the west side of the home gives you tons of storage.
